{"tid":719302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【太古城槍擊案】疑兇俄羅斯槍網問購槍　留言曝光","createTime":"2018-06-27T10:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T15:41:31.000Z","uid":2644,"like":49,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"1c2e04f331a4989a3fac7e96b0bb469ee51fd4e3","tid":719302,"uid":2644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T10:17:58.000Z","msg":"Source: 賣港01<br />\n<br />\n【太古城槍擊案】疑兇早有預謀？　俄羅斯槍網問購槍　留言曝光<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1586271/org/d234c6f40213721e51e760c9c0c84796.jpeg/eBb4gNCC30PLZa0wzy5qo2M7-jdfqWtChKpl_oSqZf4?v=w1120r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1586271%2Forg%2Fd234c6f40213721e51e760c9c0c84796.jpeg%2FeBb4gNCC30PLZa0wzy5qo2M7-jdfqWtChKpl_oSqZf4%3Fv%3Dw1120r16_9&h=88fcad01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n44歲女保鑣詹心桀，疑因爭產問題，昨午於鰂魚涌公園，涉槍傷阿姨及舅父。打扮男性化的她，洋名叫Ada。她看似「周身刀」，身份多變，除開設網站推廣其保鑣公司外，亦開設多個網店，聲稱自己是女攝影師；亦自稱在上海開設旅遊服務公司及協助內地人來港注射疫苗；她更在facebook推廣其海量的模型槍，同時亦聲稱可組團往海外「實彈射擊」，3日兩夜開價2.8萬元。<br />\n<br />\n香港01記者追查下亦發現，年前她曾搜羅多個俄羅斯的槍械網及影片網，留下電郵聯絡，公然詢問誰人可以售賣手槍給她。而警方現亦調查其所持手槍的來源，不排除有人經海外購買，再「化整為零」寄港。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1586020/org/fb85363f8c02704dea432b1a1b68bb65.jpg/XG_DjkmVlytau89Clo9x_52CbeHn5emRsW61ILFutSA?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1586020%2Forg%2Ffb85363f8c02704dea432b1a1b68bb65.jpg%2FXG_DjkmVlytau89Clo9x_52CbeHn5emRsW61ILFutSA%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=60b88238&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喜歡射擊的Ada，早前曾上傳多段短片往影片串流網站，分享其在室內射擊練習場進行手槍槍擊訓練的影片。約一年前，她亦以其阿姨「詹小慧」的名字，在多個俄羅斯的槍械網開設帳號，聲稱欲購買俄羅斯製造的MP 654K二氧化碳氣槍。60歲的詹小慧在今次槍擊案中，左上臂受槍傷，現情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n瀏覽介紹真槍及滅聲器網頁　詢問誰人可賣槍給她<br />\n<br />\n她亦往<strong><ins>俄羅斯多個上載有真槍射擊短片的槍械網及影片串流網站</ins></strong>，在內以英語留言，公然詢問誰人可售賣手槍給她，並留下電郵作聯絡。其中一段是介紹Glock 18全自動手槍的短片，與Glock 17均是用上9毫米口徑的子彈，但後者為半自動手槍，是目前全球執法單位使用最多的手槍之一。而另一段則介紹槍械滅聲器。<br />\n<br />\n今次其用來射殺親友的手槍為意製Beretta 950 Jetfire，採用.25 ACP口徑子彈，由於該些子彈菲律賓代理商代理，<strong><ins>不排除有人於菲律賓購入槍械及子彈</ins></strong>，再帶回香港。警方亦正調查其槍械及子彈的來源。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1586291/org/69dca9c057e0867d78c5d2853a239d67.jpg/k8knFH3rVzRVfHGIud_UmPiPXwW6aFkawMJeF8DCXhc?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1586291%2Forg%2F69dca9c057e0867d78c5d2853a239d67.jpg%2Fk8knFH3rVzRVfHGIud_UmPiPXwW6aFkawMJeF8DCXhc%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=b5291c2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aef717ee5a7ccde8b1c3fc9536f2dfe61f0e5138","tid":719302,"uid":189053,"like":188,"dislike":15,"score":173,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T10:24:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"980d5164dc6fe5d2fca2eb921a50b80d1e7b6eb2","tid":719302,"uid":294,"like":72,"dislike":2,"score":70,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T10:24:56.000Z","msg":"ada wait!"},{"pid":"70dbc6d5507c0d7fb53e04ff7b8882a4f53e9e4b","tid":719302,"uid":50725,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"980d5164dc6fe5d2fca2eb921a50b80d1e7b6eb2","tid":719302,"uid":294,"like":72,"dislike":2,"score":70,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T10:24:56.000Z","msg":"ada wait!"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T10:28:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712c0dec46b4bfbdbab27d58cb1ab0a6b4c988df","tid":719302,"uid":31521,"like":63,"dislike":2,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T10:28:56.000Z","msg":"香港又損失一個人才"},{"pid":"23b4c55e29bfcd4e4fd3b8175dd3e722970d0dba","tid":719302,"uid":17646,"like":101,"dislike":6,"score":95,"quote":{"pid":"aef717ee5a7ccde8b1c3fc9536f2dfe61f0e5138","tid":719302,"uid":189053,"like":188,"dislike":15,"score":173,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T10:24:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T10:29:15.000Z","msg":"在內以英語留言"},{"pid":"887f9bfab222292d4d56c7e99ee5e5c86c5fe6fc","tid":719302,"uid":72457,